The Magaluf Weekender (UK)

Season 3, Episode 6 of 6

A trio of lads from Manchester and three Newport girls check into the Lively Hotel, and rep Jordan is thrilled to finally welcome some Welsh guests to Magaluf. Meanwhile, as the boys try to cheer Ellis up and help him move on from an ex-girlfriend, a season's worth of tension comes to a head for the rep team. 

Last in the series!
